name: Custom Gouache Portrait 12"x16"
description:
My custom portraits are so much fun to make! I've done pets, kids, a restaurant and adults. The paintings start from an idea from you that I put together with some of my own added finishes. When it's complete you get to come up with a story about your painting. Order more than one and you can create an original comic strip on your wall. The 12"X16" is the most popular size. 

Each portrait is painted in my signature style in gouache on a ready to hang art board. Paintings are sprayed with a gloss varnish for protection and shine. I offer other sizes too...If you don't see a size you want talk to me. 

Once you have paid for your painting please email a photo (or a link to photos) to use for reference. Please send simple, clear photos (leave the artistry to me). Feel free to include any info you may want me to use as inspiration in the portrait as well (hobbies of subject, favorite food, time of year, place, anything you can think of). Custom paintings take approximately one month to complete. 

My email: info@ornaglyphology.com

name: Chicken Head Felt Pin (3 Options)
description:
These lovely pins were created based on the chicken-head lady character that I put in a lot of my paintings (which I'm pretty sure was inspired by the song "Chicken Head" by Project Pat and La Chat). 

Each pin is approximately 2.5" wide x 3" high. They are hand-sewn from acrylic felt (made from recycled plastic bottles) thread, and metal clasp pin-backs.

name: Xiolo
description:
Here's what you get when you mix a plushform (by Shawnimals) with ornaglyphology, a Xiolo! I knocked the blank Wee Ninja shape on it's side and turned it into a bird. The backside has an ornaglyph bubble. 

Note: This is an art toy meant for display purposes only. I sprayed it with a fixative which isn't very healthy to chew on. 

Size Approx. 9"x9"x3"
Shipping insurance is included.

name: Ornaglyphology: A Coloring Book Vol. 1 (E-Book)
description:
Ornaglyphology: A Coloring Book includes 24 images for you to print out, color and arrange into comic strips! I am offering the e-book for $5 less than the hard-copy and because it is sent electronically you don't have to pay for shipping! You get a PDF file of the book that you can print out more than once (great if you have kids or mess up a page). 

Note to Parents: This coloring book does contain images of animals smoking.
